Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Carter reshuffles his team
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040bydz
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 29 Jul 1979
Carter reshuffles his closest advisers amid speculation he is preparing his election campaign team. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less